sources.title: Lawless Land (1937) JOHNNY MACK BROWN
sources.description:
Stars: Johnny Mack Brown, Louise Stanley, Ted Adams
Director: Albert Ray

A Texas Ranger arrives in town just as the sheriff is shot in the back by a mysterious outlaw!

metadata.Plot: Jeff arrives in town to see the Sheriff only to find him just killed. The culprit is Clay Wheeler. When Jeff becomes friendly with Letty, Clay sends his man Ortega to kill him. Jeff foils the attempt and gets him to confess that Clay was the killer. With only old-timers Lafe and Bill to help, Jeff heads after Clay and his gang.
metadata.Actors: Johnny Mack Brown, Louise Stanley, Ted Adams
